You're the co-founder of the War Of Insanity!

(And clear up your inbox!)

(Oops! We posted at the same time, Sampa!)
I also like your thinking about twitter.
I like dogs, and I also like your posts. You started the "Ask Mods questions about the forums" thread, and you're really friendly as well!
You are one post away from 4 digits my friend ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif). I've also seen you around the forums quite a bit. Cherry ho!
Avera9e Joe, but not your average spacefarer ![;)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif)
Dunno what it is, but low flyer sounds awesome!
Another clever idea about twitter. Keep it up!
You've done some good things on the forum!
You're an awesome guy!
I just can't figure you out...
You helped answer some of my newbie questions back when I first began KSP, a few months ago! ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
You've become very active in a short amount of time. Now, your questions were not newbie, they were the workings of a curious mind.
You play the forum games a lot, you make comedic and friendly posts, and who doesn't love dogs? ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

You joined almost 2 years after me, and have a lot more rep and a few more posts. It says something about your contributions ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
You're the one who made this thread, which was a very nice idea! ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
I love your name, and you're very freindly across the Space Lounge. Also, as I said a few pages back, I believe you were the person that took beautiful pictures of the Moon and posted it!
The fact that you're here the most often should explain what this comment should actually hold.
Your username is really cool!
I like your profile picture, it looks like a real curious Kerbal..
Keep it up!
Once again, i love dogs. And you're very nice to me as well. ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif) Thank you for your kindness!
Your signature is very inspiring! : )

You are nice. 

I'm so original.
I like your quote!
All of your posts are real interesting! Love reading them!
